{"tid":2077280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"專家：國安法之後，「普選特首」、「釋出駐軍地」","createTime":"2020-06-24T07:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T19:02:35.000Z","uid":226548,"like":7,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"99f7485679d780decf53e686f960cb122ebdf278","tid":2077280,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>國安保障做足  普選特首風險大減</strong><br />\n<br />\n要做什麼才能安撫香港人心？過去香港經歷大動盪，中央都會出台一些惠港政策，希望能協助經濟盡早復蘇。但內地經濟現在也困難重重，應該沒有餘力再向香港提供什麼「優惠政策」。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日香港人的訴求，重點不在經濟利益，政治訴求呼聲反而更大；港版國安法通過之後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">北京可以做的第一個「菩薩行動」，是重啓行政長官普選方案。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n把23條立法和普選行政長官「綑綁」，是不少政團和政評家提出過的觀點，公民黨就主張先普選特首，才進行23條立法；也有主張認為應該倒過來，先立國安法，然後再普選特首，原因是中央擔心普選會失控，無法「駕馭」行政長官，但國安法出台之後，國家安全、限制外國勢力干預都具備了基礎，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">北京應該較為放心</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n中央立「港版國安法」之後，香港仍然要為23條自行立法，過去討論的是先進行23條立法，再普選行政長官，現在並不是本地就23條立法，與普選特首的前設條件不符。實際上，港版國安法涵蓋的四宗罪，主要是中央認為對維護國家安全最重要的4項，有了這個保障，起碼已經解決了主要問題，即使本地未立23條，北京都理應放心；而要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">釋出善意，重啓普選特首是相當重要一着</span></strong>，更是落實高度自治的重要一步。<br />\n<br />\n立國安法一拖再拖，行政長官普選又何嘗不是反反覆覆，無了期地拖延。港版國安法條文由人大常委草擬，對內地關注的國安事項應有最準確的把握，配合未來國安部門可以在香港設分支機構，執法人員也可以來港執行任務，做足保障，普選特首的政治風險已大大降低，時機上看理應水到渠成。"},{"pid":"a3e8142d0b51884ae29a110fe5af55c7118808c3","tid":2077280,"uid":194325,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077187</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"712ba97facebef6a706d63243fbdff905b3f9c0a","tid":2077280,"uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>釋出用地有實際作用 也有象徵意義</strong><br />\n<br />\n中央另一個可以「顯示誠意」的決策，是釋放若干駐軍用地給特區政府，用作發展公營房屋，解決本地住屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n目前駐港部隊管理及使用的軍事用地約2700公頃，根據中英兩國政府在1994年就香港軍事用地未來用途的安排，英方軍事用地在回歸後全數轉交中方作防務用途。<br />\n釋放駐軍用地是高度敏感的議題，特區政府的官方答覆，是「按照《基本法》及《駐軍法》的規定，任何軍事用地的使用及管理均屬國防事務，由中央人民政府全權負責，不屬香港特區的事務範圍」；換言之，是「冇得傾」，沒有商量餘地。<br />\n<br />\n是否可以釋出駐軍用地，決定權不在特區政府，而北京對這個問題的考量，除了實際軍事用途，還應考慮政治效果。香港為了覓地發展，可謂用盡了九牛二虎之力，現屆政府的計劃是明日大嶼、填海1700公頃，但至今為止，連前期研究的撥款都未批出，要落實計劃可以供應土地，沒有10年以上，根本沒有可能。<br />\n<br />\n但駐軍用地都在香港，基建設施均已完備，可即時使用。中央是否願意<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">釋出土地（也是釋出善意），很視乎領導人如何評估香港的作用</span></strong>。在一片制裁聲中，香港一方面要維持「兩制」的獨特性，另一方面也需要足夠的資源推動未來各項發展，而各類資源之中，土地對香港最重要，這方面中央政府完全可以提供協助。釋出駐軍用地有實際作用，也有象徵意義，一舉兩得，何樂而不為？"},{"pid":"b3d020083664d65da63ceb02dcd464e97937029b","tid":2077280,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-06/22/42200.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2020-06%2F22%2F42200.html&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=09839c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-06/22/42200.html</a>"},{"pid":"715336cdfc2b25f233a74734b82a21592fdf11f6","tid":2077280,"uid":39838,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"緊係可以普選特狗啦<br />\n到時邊個參選奶共奶得唔夠大力就係顛覆國家政權"},{"pid":"a2912f231578b1880c89fc1a791c922c9765340e","tid":2077280,"uid":125017,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"咁天真"},{"pid":"b59705e878feba3c85bf8015ac1434a69d0c79a2","tid":2077280,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"715336cdfc2b25f233a74734b82a21592fdf11f6","tid":2077280,"uid":39838,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"緊係可以普選特狗啦<br />\n到時邊個參選奶共奶得唔夠大力就係顛覆國家政權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5e943067187ea94e54ce5b51d8e74c3b18a98b","tid":2077280,"uid":253016,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"槍決後幫你係傷口貼番兩塊膠布釋出善意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d57ef594e3be9bad07cab2d26d9fc2dd794e2f","tid":2077280,"uid":14494,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"普選左特首，香港人反口，中共可以出解放軍<br />\n立左國安法，中共反口，香港人可以點？"},{"pid":"3d41f9cc7f31d084ffc275745654481410fd2b69","tid":2077280,"uid":306914,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"當嘢老董同詩姑開嘅，係咁上吓啦，篇嘢講到尾咪又係「唔好再講國安法啦，不如支持吓美好前景啦」呢種論調！"},{"pid":"475e8e4b9f1dad6873cd0149c448b1ca05dfa015","tid":2077280,"uid":124711,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"對冧條友再幫佢做人工呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c59dcd2c1aa4fdad58968bdc0663ad804040909","tid":2077280,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"d249dfac6f6ed9d52c84c64ee637b8a600b5b38d","tid":2077280,"uid":126889,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fa5e943067187ea94e54ce5b51d8e74c3b18a98b","tid":2077280,"uid":253016,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"槍決後幫你係傷口貼番兩塊膠布釋出善意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"打完靶唔洗收返幾毫子子彈費既善意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea2bad280952f80faf81aad98bf323c5ee245ae","tid":2077280,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"菩薩行動<br />\n<br />\n哇 咁皇恩浩蕩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8766fbfdc66d9ee2a66016ecb8ab6ee20d1b1ca2","tid":2077280,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"到時想邊個當選，就拉哂其他候選人，告佢危害國家安全。想打亂國家既部署，仲唔係危害國家安全？"},{"pid":"0c62a3c19d6c43df4c5d6c961eb0e783b62e4ecc","tid":2077280,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"又玩模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863d33ec7665dba3db8f457da1146df802bed4c3","tid":2077280,"uid":174767,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"打完你一身, 之後同你講: 放心我地私文人黎, 坐底大家講道理"},{"pid":"480a5567f9b3668c7399066dc57d9bea8e31d622","tid":2077280,"uid":103325,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"菩薩行動<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢本來就係我地應得嘅，你俾返我地唔好講到好似咁大慈大悲<br />\n同埋佢地拆咗幾多廟炸咗幾多佛像？仲好意思用菩薩嚟形容自己嘅？"},{"pid":"bc65b07eecfaaa10d4127807bcce6aa9a9f192a9","tid":2077280,"uid":52228,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n咁撚皇恩浩蕩啊"},{"pid":"cdf76a76d9cb0c04e8c8c0f9e54dfdd840a5fef1","tid":2077280,"uid":271130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"小心比pr帶風向呀<br />\n<br />\n國安法換真普選<br />\n<br />\n有人信？普選特首參選人必定要面對解散同重判狗隊嘅問題 有邊個可以搞得掂？"},{"pid":"8cc03e5c911fa2d72326d4346d0518c517ac8c7b","tid":2077280,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"強姦完比粒事後藥你<br />\n<br />\n真係多L謝曬啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引渡全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e3daf37860b9c67fb95547262ec9c8747b5fa1e9","tid":2077280,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"契弟...所謂普選特首，咪又係跟831 個垃圾PLAN<br />\n比班廢柴人大選委會揀到得返2個垃圾出黎比你叫普選，普你老母咩<br />\n香港人咪發夢啦，特首基本上同佔領地總督係零分別"},{"pid":"e6085e69759c30843a2be70ade2335f035ceabba","tid":2077280,"uid":77532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3d020083664d65da63ceb02dcd464e97937029b","tid":2077280,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-06/22/42200.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2020-06%2F22%2F42200.html&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=09839c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-06/22/42200.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5epjrZt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5epjrZt.png&h=bf61b13d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0afcff9cd2a91885d4604c2dc0d9a0ae819df42b","tid":2077280,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"立咗国安法仲有需要普選特首咩？"},{"pid":"b0928dce6b3cbd855ca20646664b45b14420397a","tid":2077280,"uid":355748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"呢個係今日聽過最on9嘅野"},{"pid":"1982efa8656e3ec24e48155f9291f6cdae9a01b1","tid":2077280,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=fa083e65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"c9cc50a978bb7b3f40df0112bbed93e35cc1307c","tid":2077280,"uid":50972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"支那會識用軟功就唔會發展到今時今日呢個地步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c414c34efb466afd73a0fc64f44cfcbaa9ef373","tid":2077280,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「強姦完買包包俾你丫」<br />\n<br />\n死開啦變態佬</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1a7a574f0355e50c1c1e959e8e2925aca39e585","tid":2077280,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"反國安法，唯一出路！<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[&darr;&darr;港獨強心針&darr;&darr;]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"2ac1e081fea233047a96d7b69a37815be45f10cd","tid":2077280,"uid":129895,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:34:54.000Z","msg":"之前: 考慮特赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg